### 1.查看镜像版本

```sh
docker  search nginx
```

### 2.拉取镜像

```
docker pull nginx
```

### 3.查看镜像

```
docker images | grep nginx
```

### 4.创建挂载目录

```
mkdir nginx
cd nginx
mkdir conf
mkdir wwwroot
mkdir logs
```
```sh
